race.description: Tas Breeders Life Member Graeme Mcculloch Hcp
race.comment: Competitive. PURR SEFANEE (7) is free running and just missed the hat-trick here off comfortable wins over the trip. She was heavily bet and keeps improving. Has the outside gate to deal with here, but has the gate speed to manage. She can bounce. SISTER ROYAL (3) made it three wins on the trot winning a 60 comfortably here stepping up to a mile. Draws inside today and keeps Byrne Burke and she's flying. Will get every chance to keep the ball rolling. MILES 'N' MILES (4) went close in the PURR SEFANEE race and will be better for it. May need longer now, but has to be considered, regardless. TUSKEGEE (1) didn't finish it off here over a middle distance but won this trip on the synthetic prior. He's in the mix.
